These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, raspberry
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, blue
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, tulip
2 different games are played: monopoly, bridge
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, volleyball
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes red##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who likes blue##1
6. the person who growstulip is the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea        | hot-chocolate |
| Food          | raspberry  | pineapple     |
| Color         | blue    | red         |
| Flower           | lily    | tulip |
| Game   | monopoly  | bridge     |
| Transport           | quad-bike      | scooter    |
| Sport         | volleyball | golf          |

