2 different pets are kept: goat, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, van
1. the russian is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person who growstulip is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage         | cola      | lemonade       |
| Cigar           | tiparillo | blend |
| Food   | watermelon      | cranberry        |
| Flower   | tulip         | sunflower        |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | russian       |
| Pet           | mouse        | goat          |
| Transport     | van          | snowmobile    |

